flowchart TD
    A[resilient_completion\ncalled] --> B[Attempt 1\nclient.chat.completions.create]
    B --> C{Success?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Return response]
    C -->|RateLimitError\nAPIConnectionError\nAPITimeoutError| E[wait_random_exponential\nmultiplier=1, max=60s]
    E --> F[Attempt 2]
    F --> G{Success?}
    G -->|Yes| D
    G -->|Error again| H[wait exponential]
    H --> I[Attempt 3 ... 6]
    I --> J{Success?}
    J -->|Yes| D
    J -->|Exhausted\nstop_after_attempt 6| K[Raise last\nexception]
